reviewText: Why can't they put this on dvd
can this movie be put on DVD?
Love Marie  a Fan For Ever

I grew up with Donny and Marie and I always liked the Osmonds. I still remember the Osmonds with one of my favorite singers Andy Williams. This story is about how the Osmond family came to be. If you like the Osmonds,then you will love this gem.
I was very much into this movie, as a fan, I found it interesting to see how the Osmonds got their start. Now they need to make another to pick up where this one left off!
IT"S a great movie about THE OSMONDS every OSMOND fan should have it I sure too
I loved this movie from start to finish. I just wish it were at least a half an hour longer.
